{"tid":871648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"( 劍指中國?) 美擬降低指控「滙率操縱」門檻","createTime":"2018-10-22T06:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T06:20:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"169d26f302c2f8f0262be3d175b774dbc75c71e0","tid":871648,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"美國財政部長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）周日表示，對修改美國對滙率操縱國的認定標準持開放的態度。外界普遍認為，標準一旦修改，美方將更容易對一個經濟體標籤為「滙率操縱」，此舉矛頭直指中國。<br />\n<br />\n由於目前認定標準門檻極高，美國財政部在上周發表的半年度報告，再次沒有將中國列爲滙率操縱國，但如果美國修改認定標準，將大大增加特朗普政府將中國認定爲滙率操縱國的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2190480/%E7%BE%8E%E6%93%AC%E9%99%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%99%E7%8E%87%E6%93%8D%E7%B8%B1%E3%80%8D%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%20%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2190480%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%2593%25AC%25E9%2599%258D%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25BB%2599%25E7%258E%2587%25E6%2593%258D%25E7%25B8%25B1%25E3%2580%258D%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25AA%25BB%2520%25E7%259F%259B%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E7%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=616389cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2190480/%E7%BE%8E%E6%93%AC%E9%99%8D%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E3%80%8C%E6%BB%99%E7%8E%87%E6%93%8D%E7%B8%B1%E3%80%8D%E9%96%80%E6%AA%BB%20%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E7%9B%B4%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"}]}